divs: Sighting Detailsi was about 14yrs old,I lived in plainfield new jersey at that time,my grandmother would leave the house to go to work at around 5am,the morning that it happened was summer,clear skys,no clouds were present at that time,my grandmother came back into the house got me out of bed to go out and look at this thing,it was about cloud high,it was silver,it was not moving at that time,it was almost over the house,,,we watched it for a few minutes,than it started to go up straight up,untell we couldnt see it any more...this is when i became interested in this UFO..ect....at the time i didnt think anybody would take me serious,on top of that WHO DO YOU TELL,my grandmother felt the same...the reason why i am telling my story now is because of MUFON,and the fact that there is a place to tell people about this,,I AM NOT CRAZY,,i worked in the medical field for 25yrs. thank you for MUFON...............................
